metadata.name: FREEDOM FIGHTER
metadata.description:
"Freedom you're the bird flying in the sky, so how can I reach you when you are flying and I'm creeping on the ground" 
Freedom is a dream for many people, and this is the story of a girl who is a freedom fighter. She has become fed up with struggling to survive in a sark world and decides to sacrifice her life and give her blood to make this dream come true.
